<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.2.3">
<l>tantam makka ḷaḻutu ceṉṟāl tāymā rāvār tarikka killār</l>
<l>vantu niṉmēṟ pūcal ceyya vāḻa valla vācu tēvā</l>
<l>untai yāruṉ tiṟatta ralla ruṉṉai nāṉoṉ ṟurappa māṭṭēṉ</l>
<l>nanta kōpa ṉaṇici ṟuvā nāṉcu ranta mulaiyu ṇāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If their children go [about] crying,</l>
<l>when their mothers who are unable to bear [it]</l>
<l>come to complain about you, you are able to thrive, O Vācudeva!</l>
<l>Your father cannot reveal you [and]</l>
<l>I am unable to be furious at you about [even] one thing.</l>
<l>O little one, jewel of Nandagōpaṉ, drink from my swollen breasts!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
